msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Furaha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Fahari"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When we stay calm, share how we feel, and look for solutions together, it will help us all ‚Äì even if we are not sure of the right outcome. You can learn to manage tricky situations and problems together with your teen."
msgstr "Tunapokuwa watulivu, tukishirikisha watu jinsi tunavyohisi, na kutafuta suluhu pamoja, itatusaidia sisi sote - hata kama hatuna uhakika wa matokeo sahihi. Unaweza kujifunza kumudu hali na matatizo magumu kwa pamoja na kijana wako."

