msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f1_mother.name did well by finding solutions together with @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. But this can be hard to do.\n"
"\n"
"Many parents want to help their teens but find it difficult to talk about sensitive topics, like body changes and relationships."
msgstr ""
"@data.characters.f1_mother.name walifanya vizuri kutafuta suluhu pamoja na @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. Lakini inaweza kuwa ngumu kufanya.\n"
"\n"
"Wazazi wengi wanataka kuwasaidia vijana lakini hupata ugumu kuongea kuhusu mada nyeti, kama mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano ya kimapenzi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some questions from other parents to help you begin."
msgstr "Hapa kuna baadhi ya maswali kutoka kwa wazazi wengine kukusaidia kuanza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Who should start the conversation about body changes and intimate relationships? \n"
"Try selecting each option for more tips!"
msgstr ""
"Nani aanze mazungumzo kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano ya kimapenzi?\n"
"Jaribu kuchagua kila chaguo kwa vidokezo zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The teen's friend"
msgstr "Rafiki wa kijana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The teen"
msgstr "Kijana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The parent"
msgstr "Mzazi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is not quite right. \n"
"\n"
"Remember, friends can sometimes mislead or have wrong information themselves."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sahihi kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka, marafiki muda mwingine wanaweza kupotoshana au kuwa na taarifa za uongo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is not quite right. \n"
"\n"
"Your teen might feel uncomfortable or scared to start that conversation with you."
msgstr ""
"Hii sio sawa kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Kijana wako anaweza kuhisi wasiwasi au kuogopa kuanzisha mazungumzo hayo na wewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, you may need to start the conversation - and it‚Äôs okay to feel shy. Be open and use the right words for any body parts you discuss (like breasts, penis, or vagina).\n"
"\n"
"You can practise with a friend and ask a health worker or social worker for more information. The more you know, the better you can help your teen.\n"
"\n"
"And remember, it‚Äôs also okay not to know everything. You can say, ‚ÄúI‚Äôm not sure - let me find out and tell you later.‚Äù"
msgstr ""
"Ndio, unaweza kuhitajia kuanza mazungumzo ‚Äî na ni sawa kujihisi aibu. Kuwa wazi na tumia maneno sahihi unapozungumzia sehemu za mwili (kama matiti, uume, au uke).\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza pia kufanya mazoezi na rafiki na kuuliza mhudumu wa afya au mfanyakazi wa kijamii kwa taarifa zaidi. Kadri unavyojua zaidi, ndivyo utakavyoweza kumsaidia kijana wako vizuri zaidi.\n"
"\n"
"Na kumbuka, pia ni sawa kutokuwa na majibu yote. Unaweza kusema, ‚ÄúSijui hakika ‚Äî acha nitafute taarifa na nitakujulisha baadae.‚Äù"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Other parents also wonder:"
msgstr "Wazazi wengine pia wanashangaa:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When is the right time to start talking about body changes and intimate relationships?\n"
"Try selecting each option for more tips!"
msgstr ""
"Ni upi wakati mwafaka wa kuanza kuzungumza kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano ya kimapenzi?\n"
"Jaribu kuchagua kila chaguo kupata vidokezo zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When you find out they have a boyfriend or girlfriend"
msgstr "Ukigundua kuwa wana rafiki wa kiume au rafiki wa kike"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When they turn 10"
msgstr "Wakifikisha miaka 10"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Before they turn 10"
msgstr "Kabla hawajafikisha miaka 10"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When you get an opportunity"
msgstr "Unapopata fursa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs not quite right.\n"
"\n"
"Teens need to learn about body changes and relationships early, so they are prepared and can make good choices.\n"
"\n"
"If you find out your teen is having sex, try to stay calm and share your worries gently. Getting angry can make it harder for your teen to talk to you."
msgstr ""
"Hii sio sawa kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana wanahitaji kujifunza kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano mapema, ili wawe tayari na waweze kufanya maamuzi mazuri.\n"
"\n"
"Kama utagundua kuwa kijana wako amefanya mapenzi, jaribu kubaki mtulivu na kushirikisha wasiwasi wako kwa upole. Kukasirika kunaweza kumfanya kijana wako ashindwe kuzungumza nawe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Age 10 is when a lot of children start to enter puberty, so they need to already understand how their bodies and feelings may change.\n"
"\n"
"This will also help them cope better with sexual feelings safely."
msgstr ""
"Umri wa miaka 10 ndiyo wakati watoto wengi huanza kubarehe, hivyo vijana wanapaswa tayari kuelewa jinsi miili yao na hisia zao zinavyoweza kubadilika.\n"
"\n"
"Hii pia itawasaidia kukabiliana vyema na hisia za kingono kwa usalama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That's right! \n"
"\n"
"Age 10 is when a lot of children start to enter puberty, so they need to already understand how their bodies and feelings may change.\n"
"\n"
"This will also help them cope better with sexual feelings safely."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sawa!\n"
"\n"
"Umri wa miaka 10 ndiyo wakati watoto wengi huanza kuingia kwenye umri barehe, hivyo vijana wanapaswa tayari kuelewa jinsi miili yao na hisia zao zinavyoweza kubadilika.\n"
"\n"
"Hii pia itawasaidia kukabiliana vyema na hisia za kingono kwa usalama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It‚Äôs good to start talking about body changes and relationships early - by gently answering your child‚Äôs questions.\n"
"\n"
"You don‚Äôt need to explain everything. Just give simple, honest answers that match their age and understanding."
msgstr ""
"Ni vizuri kuanza kuzungumzia kuhusu mabadiliko ya kimwili na mahusiano mapema-kwa kujibu kwa utulivu maswali ya kijana wako.\n"
"\n"
"Hauhitaji kuelezea kila kitu. Mpe jibu rahisi, aminifu ambalo linaendana na umri wao na uelewa wao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Many parents also ask:"
msgstr "Wazazi wengi pia wanauliza:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"How can I best keep my teen safe?\n"
"Try selecting each option for more tips!"
msgstr ""
"Ninawezaje kumweka kijana wangu salama vizuri zaidi?\n"
"Jaribu kuchagua kila chaguo kwa kupata vidokezo zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I determine what my teen can and cannot do"
msgstr "Ninaamua kile ambacho kijana wangu anaweza na hawezi kufanya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I keep information or bad influences away from them"
msgstr "Ninaweka taarifa au ushawishi mbaya mbali nao"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I build a healthy trusting relationship with my teen"
msgstr "Ninatengeneza uhusiano mzuri wa kuaminika na wenye afya pamoja na kijana wangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I discuss consequences and solutions with my teen"
msgstr "Ninajadili madhara na suluhisho pamoja na kijana wangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I emphasize that pressure is never okay"
msgstr "Nasisitiza kuwa shinikizo halikubaliki kamwe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This may not work.\n"
"\n"
"When we try to control too much, teens may do the opposite of what we want.\n"
"\n"
"But when we guide them and give them space to make choices, they often act more responsibly."
msgstr ""
"Hii inaweza isifanye kazi.\n"
"\n"
"Tunapojaribu kudhibiti sana, vijana wanaweza kufanya kinyume na tunachotaka.\n"
"\n"
"Lakini tunapowaongoza na kuwapa nafasi ya kufanya maamuzi, mara nyingi hufanya mambo kwa uwajibikaji zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This may not work. \n"
"\n"
"Teens get pressure and information from many places we can‚Äôt control.\n"
"\n"
"As parents, we can guide and prepare them to know what is right or wrong‚Äîand help them feel confident to make good decisions."
msgstr ""
"Hii inaweza isifanye kazi.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana hupata shinikizo na taarifa kutoka sehemu nyingi ambazo hatuwezi kuzidhibiti.\n"
"\n"
"Kama wazazi, tunaweza kuwaongoza na kuwaandaa wajue kilicho sawa na kisicho sawa‚Äîna kuwasaidia kujihisi kujiamini kufanya maamuzi bora."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right.\n"
"\n"
"When your teen feels trusted, they are more likely to trust you and come to you for advice or help.\n"
"\n"
"Praise and thank them when they share. Avoid judging, so they feel safe to talk to you again."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni kweli.\n"
"\n"
"Wakati kijana wako anahisi kuaminika, kuna uwezekano mkubwa kukuamini na kuja kwako kwa ushauri au msaada.\n"
"\n"
"Mpongeze na mshukuru anapokushirkisha. Epuka kumhukumu, ili ahisi salama kuzungumza nawewe tena."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right.\n"
"\n"
"Good decisions come from thinking through the consequences. Talk openly with your teen when there‚Äôs a problem. Listen to each other and find solutions together.\n"
"\n"
"Each challenge is an opportunity to teach your teen that actions have consequences‚Äîand you can handle them as a team.\n"
"\n"
"Remember to praise each other for working through tough situations together."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sawa.\n"
"\n"
"Maamuzi mazuri hutokea kwa kufikiria matokeo. Zungumza kwa uwazi na kijana wako pale mnapokumbana na tatizo. Sikilizaneni ninyi kwa ninyi na tafuteni suluhisho pamoja.\n"
"\n"
"Kila changamoto ni nafasi ya kumfundisha kijana wako kwamba matendo yana matokeo‚Äîna kwamba mnaweza kuyakabili kwa pamoja kama timu.\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka kupongezana kwa kushirikiana kwa kupitia hali ngumu pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right.\n"
"\n"
"To stay safe, your teen needs to know the difference between respectful behaviours and relationships, and unhealthy ones..\n"
"\n"
"Respectful relationships feel caring, safe, and fair. Unhealthy ones involve pressure, discomfort, or feeling unsafe.\n"
"\n"
"No one should be forced to do something they‚Äôre not okay with. You can learn more about this in the Staying Safe module."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sawa.\n"
"\n"
"Kubaki salama, kijana wako anahitaji kuelewa tofauti kati ya tabia na mahusiano ya heshima, na yale yasiyo na afya.\n"
"\n"
"Mahusiano ya heshima huhisi kuwa ya upendo, salama, na ya haki. Mahusiano yasiyo na afya hujumuisha shinikizo, hali ya kutokuwa na furaha, au kuhisi kutokuwa salama.\n"
"\n"
"Hakuna mtu anayepaswa kulazimishwa kufanya jambo ambalo hakubaliani nalo. Unaweza kujifunza zaidi kuhusu hili katika mada ya Kubaki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Another common question among parents:"
msgstr "Swali lingine lililozoeleka miongoni mwa wazazi:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"How can I help prevent my teen from having sex too young?\n"
"Try selecting each option for more tips!"
msgstr ""
"Ninawezaje kusaidia kumzuia kijana wangu kufanya ngono akiwa bado mdogo?\n"
"Jaribu kuchagua kila chaguo kupata vidokezo zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keep any information about sex away from them"
msgstr "Weka taaarifa za ngono mbali nao"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Forbid them to have a boyfriend or girlfriend"
msgstr "Kuwakataza kua na rafiki wa kike au kiume"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Have an open discussion on how and why they could wait to have sex"
msgstr "Fanya mazungumzo ya wazi kuhusu kivipi na kwa nini wanaweza kusubiri kabla ya kufanya ngono"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs not quite right.\n"
"\n"
"Teens hear many things about sex‚Äîfrom school, friends, or social media. Some of it is wrong.\n"
"\n"
"Knowing about sex doesn‚Äôt mean they are having sex. Good information helps them stay safe and understand why waiting to have sex can be a good choice.\n"
"\n"
"Without this knowledge, they may face problems, like not knowing how pregnancy happens or the risks of sex."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo sio sahihi kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana husikia mambo mengi kuhusu ngono‚Äîkutoka shuleni, kwa marafiki, au kwenye mitandao ya kijamii. Baadhi ya taarifa hizo si sahihi.\n"
"\n"
"Kujua kuhusu ngono haimaanishi kwamba wanafanya ngono. Taarifa sahihi huwasaidia kuwa salama na kuelewa kwa nini kusubiri kabla ya kufanya ngono kunaweza kuwa uamuzi mzuri.\n"
"\n"
"bila maarifa, wanaweza kukumbana na matatizo, kama kutokujua kwa namna gani mimba inatokea au hatari vya ngono."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs not quite right.\n"
"\n"
"Your teen might have a boyfriend or girlfriend and not tell you.\n"
"\n"
"If you make them hide it, they may not come to you with questions or problems‚Äîand this can lead to risky situations."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo si sahihi kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Kijana wako anaweza kuwa na mpenzi na asiwe amekuambia.\n"
"\n"
"Kama ukiwalazimisha kuficha uhusiano huo, wanaweza wasikushirikishe maswali au matatizo yao‚Äîna hili linaweza kuwapelekea kwenye hali za hatari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right.\n"
"\n"
"Teens are figuring out who they are. They look to friends and media for answers, and may feel pressure to do things they‚Äôre not ready for.\n"
"\n"
"Talk calmly with your teen about waiting to have sex until they feel ready, are in a safe relationship, and understand the consequences. Focus on guiding them calmly to make healthy choices."
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sawa.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana wanajaribu kujitambua wao ni akina nani. Huwaangalia marafiki na vyombo vya habari kutafuta majibu, na wanaweza kuhisi shinikizo la kufanya mambo ambayo hawajawa tayari kuyafanya.\n"
"\n"
"Zungumza kwa utulivu na kijana wako kuhusu kusubiri kufanya ngono hadi pale atakapojihisi yuko tayari, yuko kwenye uhusiano salama, na anaelewa matokeo ya maamuzi yake. Lenga kuwaongoza kwa utulivu ili wafanye maamuzi yenye afya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Discussing body changes and intimate relationships can be uncomfortable, but it is so important in order to keep your teen happy, healthy and safe. \n"
"\n"
"Here are some skills to help you get started."
msgstr ""
"Kujadili kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano ya kimapenzi kunaweza kuwa kwa hali ya kutokuwa na raha, lakini ni muhimu sana ili kuhakikisha kijana wako anakuwa mwenye furaha, afya njema, na salama.\n"
"\n"
"Hapa kuna baadhi ya ujuzi wa kukusaidia kuanza mazungumzo hayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BUILD"
msgstr "KUJENGA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Build a strong relationship with your teen by spending time with them and showing them you trust them. Create a safe, encouraging space, and avoid judging them.\n"
"\n"
"That will make your teen share their questions and worries with you, when they need advice or are in a potentially dangerous situation."
msgstr ""
"Jenga uhusiano mzuri na kijana wako kwa kutumia muda pamoja naye na kuwaonyesha kuwa unamwamini. Unda nafasi salama, ya kutia moyo, na uepuke kuwahukumu.\n"
"\n"
"Hilo litamfanya kijana wako ashiriki maswali na mahangaiko yake nawe, anapohitaji ushauri au yuko katika hali inayoweza kuwa hatari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "START"
msgstr "ANZA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your teen may feel shy or scared, so parents need to start the talk about body changes and intimate relationships.\n"
"\n"
"Begin early by answering questions simply and honestly. This builds confidence for you and your child.\n"
"\n"
"It‚Äôs okay to feel uncomfortable. Be open, use the correct words, and get help if you don‚Äôt know all the answers."
msgstr ""
"Kijana wako anaweza kuhisi aibu au hofu, hivyo ni jukumu la mzazi kuanzisha mazungumzo kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano ya kimapenzi.\n"
"\n"
"Anza mapema kwa kujibu maswali kwa urahisi na kwa uaminifu. Hii hujenga kujiamini kwako na kwa mtoto wako.\n"
"\n"
"Ni sawa kuhisi kutokuwa na raha. Kuwa wazi, tumia maneno sahihi, na tafuta msaada kama hujui majibu yote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "GUIDE"
msgstr "MWONGOZO"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your teen will hear about sex from many places. If they feel safe with you, you can help them find good information and make smart choices.\n"
"\n"
"Help them think about consequences without shame or blame. Make sure they know they should never feel pressure (or pressure others) into sex or a relationship.\n"
"\n"
"You can also ask other adults or health workers for help and information."
msgstr ""
"Kijana wako atasikia kuhusu ngono kutoka sehemu nyingi. Ikiwa wanajihisi salama na wewe, unaweza kuwasaidia kupata taarifa sahihi na kufanya maamuzi ya busara.\n"
"\n"
"Wasaidie kufikiria kuhusu matokeo ya maamuzi yao bila aibu wala lawama. Hakikisha anajua kuwa hapaswi kulazimishwa (wala kumlazimisha mtu mwingine) kuingia kwenye ngono au uhusiano.\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza pia kuomba msaada na taarifa kutoka kwa watu wazima wengine au wahudumu wa afya."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week‚Äôs home activity is to read and talk about this module‚Äôs stories with your teen. Use them to start a conversation about body changes and relationships.\n"
"\n"
"You can talk about what happened with @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name or @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name and their parents.\n"
"\n"
"These stories can make it easier to talk about tricky topics and share ideas about healthy, respectful relationships."
msgstr ""
"Shughuli ya nyumbani ya wiki hii ni kusoma na kujadili hadithi za mada hii pamoja na kijana wako. Zitumie kama njia ya kuanzisha mazungumzo kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano.\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza kuzungumza kile kilichotea kwa @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name au @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name na wazazi wao.\n"
"\n"
"Hadithi hizi zinaweza kufanya iwe rahisi kuzungumza kuhusu mada ngumu na kushirikishana mawazo kuhusu mahusiano yenye afya na ya kuheshimiana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you read the stories with your teen and use them to start an open talk about body changes and relationships?"
msgstr "Je, unaweza kusoma hadithi hizi pamoja na kijana wako na kuzitumia kuanzisha mazungumzo ya wazi kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Perfect! Talking about these topics openly helps your teen feel safe, supported, and able to make healthy decisions."
msgstr "Vizuri sana! Kuzungumza kuhusu mada hizi kwa uwazi humsaidia kijana wako kujihisi salama, kupata msaada, na kuwa na uwezo wa kufanya maamuzi yenye afya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are doing so well! Even starting a small conversation makes a big difference. Keep going - your teen will appreciate your support."
msgstr "Unafanya vizuri sana! Hata kuanzisha mazungumzo madogo kunaweza kuleta mabadiliko makubwa. Endelea ‚Äî kijana wako atathamini msaada wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. It is normal for these talks to feel a little uncomfortable at first. Try again another time - every small step counts."
msgstr "Ni sawa. Ni kawaida kwa mazungumzo haya kuhisi kutokuwa na raha mwanzoni. Jaribu tena wakati mwingine ‚Äî kila hatua ndogo ina maana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Talking openly with your teen about body changes and relationships helps them feel safe, supported, and better able to make healthy choices. \n"
"\n"
"No matter your teen‚Äôs age, now is the best time to build trust and guide them with care."
msgstr ""
"Kuzungumza kwa uwazi na kijana wako kuhusu mabadiliko ya mwili na mahusiano huwasaidia kujihisi salama, kupata msaada, na kuwa na uwezo bora wa kufanya maamuzi yenye afya.\n"
"\n"
"Haijalishi umri wa kijana wako, sasa ni wakati mwafaka wa kujenga uaminifu na kuwaongoza kwa kujali."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.media_daughter_8.name learned a lot from honest talks with her mother. Tap play to hear their story"
msgstr "@data.characters.media_daughter_8.name alijifunza mengi kutoka kwa mazungumzo ya uaminifu na mama yake. Bonyeza kucheza kusikiliza hadithi yao"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"As teens, we hear all these things about sex from others at school and on the internet. I thought all those things were true, and I was doing a lot of things secretly, because my friends were pushing me and I was afraid of what my mother would say.\n"
"\n"
"When I did this app together with my mother, I realised that so many things I learnt were not true. I learnt I can get better information and I learnt others should never push me to do things I do not want to do. My mother and I can talk about these things now. I wish we could have done that when I was younger, because it would have helped me a lot, but I am still glad we can talk today. Whenever I have a question or problem now, I know I can ask my mother and she will help me think of answers and solutions together."
msgstr ""
"Kama vijana, tunasikia mambo mengi kuhusu ngono kutoka kwa wengine shuleni na mtandaoni. Nilidhani yote hayo ni kweli, na nilikuwa nafanya mengi kwa usiri, kwa sababu marafiki zangu walikuwa wananishawishi na nilikuwa naogopa kwamba mama yangu atasema nini.\n"
"\n"
"Nilipopitia programu hii pamoja na mama, niligundua kwamba mengi niliyojifunza yalikuwa sio kweli. Nilijifunza naweza kupata taarifa nzuri zaidi na nilijifunza wengine wasinisukume kufanya jambo ambalo nisilotaka kufanya. Mimi na mama yangu tunaweza kuongelea haya mambo kwa sasa. Nilitamani tungeweza fanya haya nilipokuwa mtoto, kwa sababu ingenisaidia sana, lakini bado ninafurahi tunaweza kuzungumza leo. Kila ninapokuwa na swali au tatizo sasa, ninajua naweza kumuuliza mama yangu na atanisaidia kufikiria majibu na suluhisho kwa pamoja."

